## How to Run It

From now on, you no longer need to run `python language_router.py`. 

To launch the app:
1. Open a terminal in the `model/color_model/` folder.
2. Run the command:
   ```bash
   python api.py
   ```
3. It will start the server and print: `🚀 Starting MangaLens API Server on http://localhost:8000`
4. Open your web browser and go to `http://localhost:8000` to see the new UI.

> [!TIP]
> The heavy lifting (AI models) runs in the background. If you close the terminal running `api.py`, the app will shut down.
